data.description:
Welcome to your coastal dream lifestyle! This stunning 2Br/2.5BA townhome is nestled in a highly desirable location, a mere 3 blocks away from the sparkling ocean, offering the perfect blend of tranquility and beachside living.  1 bedroom and full bath downstairs offers privacy from the 2nd bedroom and 1 1/2 bathrooms upstairs.  Enjoy the beautiful Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring throughout. Cozy up to the wood-burning fireplace in your family room. All stainless steel appliances and newer bathroom vanities upgraded in 2020.  Fenced in backyard!
Walk to the beach, shops or restaurants effortlessly without the hassle of driving.
Bask in the warmth of this home's natural sunlight creating a bright and inviting atmosphere. 
Step outside and feel the sand between your toes within minutes. Whether you're a morning beachcomber or a sunset enthusiast, living so close to the ocean ensures you can savor every moment. Don't miss your opportunity to make this townhome your own slice of paradise!
